      "name": "Patient Health Questionnaire-9",
      "description": "The PHQ-9 relates to the 9 MDD (Major Depressive Disorder) module of the full PHQ and helps to assess the patient\u0027s degree of depression. The tool has an additional question which is not scored, but which helps the clinician get a sense of how impactful these symptoms are on their patient\u0027s life."
